{"tid":276763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府刊憲：禁止向未滿18歲人士售賣和供應令人醺醉酒類","createTime":"2017-06-09T05:20:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-09T05:30:11.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"28ed1c3be8e7bdda29d1f96e8da4c68926215812","tid":276763,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T05:20:50.000Z","msg":"政府今日就《應課稅品(修訂)條例草案》刊憲，禁止向未滿18歲人士售賣和供應令人醺醉酒類，並規定在互聯網、電話或郵遞方式賣酒，要收到買方的年齡聲明，違例者可以罰款。<br />\n<br />\n食物及衞生局副局長陳肇始表示，法例生效後執法工作將交由控酒辦負責，當局會派便衣人員，主動巡查賣酒黑點。酒吧業界希望，政府對便利店賣酒的監管與酒吧標準看齊。"},{"pid":"0ecd20e051f4ba988d738e717a170b1f9395ab66","tid":276763,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T05:21:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1335092-20170609.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1335092-20170609.htm&d=AbalyyZSjWnhX2IyPP99JBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=2c5757c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1335092-20170609.htm&h=3629db74\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1335092-20170609.htm</a>"},{"pid":"400a521b69a04e1c007b2897db7b575c69816d7a","tid":276763,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T05:30:11.000Z","msg":"煮食用酒包括在內？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}